Standard Android Git Ignore File for Kotlin/Java Projects

----------------------------------

1. BUILD/OUTPUT ARTIFACTS

/build
/out
/captures
.externalNativeBuild
.cxx
/merged-not-compiled-resources
/intermediates
/generated
/dexedLibs
/apks/
/aab/

Output of gradlew dependencies

dependencies.txt

JVM and Class files

*.jar
*.class
*.so
*.o
*.bin  # Explicitly ignoring all bin files as requested

2. ANDROID STUDIO / IDE SPECIFIC

Gradle

.gradle
gradle-app.setting

Local configuration

local.properties
.tab # Explicitly ignoring all tab files as requested
.DS_Store

IntelliJ / Android Studio files

*.iml
*.iws
*.ipr
.idea/workspace.xml
.idea/libraries
.idea/modules.xml
.idea/assetWizardSettings.xml
.idea/navEditor.xml
.idea/caches/
.idea/codeStyles/

Exclude the entire .idea folder except for files you want to share (e.g., code styles)

If you want to share specific .idea files, uncomment them below:

.idea/inspectionProfiles/

.idea/vcs.xml

3. KOTLIN SPECIFIC

Kotlin annotation processing (kapt) output

/kapt
/ksp

4. TESTING AND COVERAGE

Unit test coverage reports

/coverage
/jacoco

5. MERGER FILES (Requested by User)

Merger outputs are usually in the build directory, but this ensures they are ignored globally

*merger.xml
*merger.json
*merger.txt
merger